Description: CVE-2026-42959 - Crash during DNSSEC validation of malicious content
 Replace orig->ns_numrrsets with chase->ns_numrrsets in val_fill_reply()
 ADDITIONAL section processing to prevent dereferencing an uninitialized
 chase->rrsets[] slot.
 .
 Note: upstream regression test (testdata/fill_reply_uninit.rpl from commit
 d357935) is omitted because it was authored against unbound 1.25.1 and its
 expected-answer block does not match the validator state-machine output of
 1.17.1, even though the underlying bug is fixed.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/NLnetLabs/unbound/commit/94d5bab
Author: NLnet Labs
Last-Update: 2026-06-03
